'''East London''' ([[Afrikaans]]: Oos-Londen, [[Sethosa]]: eMonti) ke toropo kgolo o ka borwa-boshabela mo diporofense [[Kapa Bohlabela]] (Eastern Cape) kamoka [[Afrika Borwa]] mô [[Buffalo City Metropolitan Municipality]]. 

Motse larileng ka ka [[Indian Ocean]] lebōpong la leoatle, haholo-holo pakeng tša Buffalo River le Nahoon River, le mabotho a se boletseng ba naha eo feela nōka koung. East London kajeno nang le baahi ba ka 267.000 le ka 755.000 ka lefelo la ditoropong.
